---
// Privacy policy (EN mirror of /datenschutz.html — same slug so the language
// switcher pairs the pages). Describes factually what this static site does.
// [TODO] fields must be filled before publishing.
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteNav from '../../components/SiteNav.astro';
import Attribution from '../../components/Attribution.astro';
---
<Layout title={"Privacy Policy | VerseBase"} description={"Privacy policy of VerseBase: a static website without cookies or tracking — what data is processed when visiting, when external images load, and when YouTube videos are clicked."} themeColor="#05070d" translated={true}>
<style is:inline>
:root{--bg:#05070d;--bg-2:#0a0e18;--surface:#0f1524;--surface-2:#141c30;--accent:#2dd4ff;--accent-2:#6ea8ff;--text:#e8eefc;--muted:#8a99b8;--line:rgba(110,168,255,.16);--line-soft:rgba(232,238,252,.10);--ink:#05070d;--maxw:840px;}
.lg-wrap{max-width:var(--maxw);margin:0 auto;padding:3.2rem 1.25rem 4rem}
.lg-wrap h1{font-family:var(--font-display);font-weight:900;font-size:clamp(2rem,6vw,3rem);color:#fff;margin:0 0 1.6rem}
.lg-wrap h2{font-family:var(--font-ui);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.95rem;color:var(--accent);margin:2.2rem 0 .6rem;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);padding-bottom:.4rem}
.lg-wrap p, .lg-wrap li{color:var(--text);line-height:1.7;font-size:.98rem}
.lg-wrap ul{padding-left:1.2rem}
.lg-wrap .muted{color:var(--muted)}
.lg-fill{display:inline-block;background:color-mix(in srgb,#ff5b5b 14%,transparent);border:1px dashed #ff5b5b;border-radius:4px;padding:0 .45rem;color:#ffb4b4;font-weight:700}
</style>
<SiteNav crumbs={[{ label: 'Archive', href: '/index.html' }, { label: 'Privacy' }]} hasEn={true} />
<main id="main">
  <div class="lg-wrap">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <h2>Controller</h2>
    <p>
      <span class="lg-fill">[TODO: Full name]</span>, <span class="lg-fill">[TODO: Address]</span> —
      e-mail: <a href="mailto:krysx141@gmail.com">krysx141@gmail.com</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Principle</h2>
    <p>
      This website is a purely static, non-commercial fan project. It uses <strong>no cookies</strong>,
      <strong>no analytics or tracking services</strong>, no advertising, no contact forms and no
      comment functions. No personal data is transmitted to, stored or shared by us.
    </p>

    <h2>Server log files (hosting)</h2>
    <p>
      When you visit this website, the hosting provider
      <span class="lg-fill">[TODO: hosting provider, e.g. Cloudflare Pages]</span> technically
      processes connection data (IP address, timestamp, requested resource, user agent) in server
      logs. Legal basis: Art. 6 (1) (f) GDPR (legitimate interest in secure operation).
    </p>

    <h2>Local browser storage (localStorage)</h2>
    <p>
      Some tools on this site (e.g. the crafting planner, “owned” marks, view settings) store their
      state exclusively <strong>locally in your browser</strong> (localStorage). This data never
      leaves your device and can be deleted at any time via your browser settings.
    </p>

    <h2>Externally embedded images</h2>
    <p>
      Some imagery is loaded from external sources. When these images are fetched, your IP address
      is technically transmitted to the respective provider:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>fleetyards.net</strong> — ship and vehicle imagery</li>
      <li><strong>starcitizen.tools / cstone.space</strong> — individual media assets</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Ambient background videos</h2>
    <p>
      Some pages show short, muted video loops (trailer excerpts) as backgrounds. These files
      are served <strong>locally by this website</strong> — no third-party server is contacted.
      With reduced motion enabled (prefers-reduced-motion), an active data-saver mode, or on
      small screens, only the still image is loaded instead.
    </p>

    <h2>YouTube videos (click to load)</h2>
    <p>
      Videos are embedded as preview stills and load <strong>only after you click</strong>, via
      youtube-nocookie.com (Google Ireland Ltd.). Before the click, no connection to Google is made;
      after the click, <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" rel="noopener">Google’s privacy policy</a> applies.
    </p>

    <h2>Fonts</h2>
    <p>All web fonts are served locally by this website. No connection to Google Fonts is made.</p>

    <h2>Your rights</h2>
    <p class="muted">
      You have the rights under Art. 15–21 GDPR (access, rectification, erasure, restriction, data
      portability, objection) and the right to lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority
      (Art. 77 GDPR). Since this website does not collect or store personal data about you, access
      requests will usually come up empty — if in doubt, reach out by e-mail.
    </p>
  </div>
</main>
<Attribution sources={[]} />
</Layout>
